name: Tri-World
description:
Description
Artwork by "Sahred Toy"
14567 × 9047 px
.
We are all different. We hold different beliefs. But there are always common threads that bind us together. This work depicts a shared belief of tri-world--heaven, earth and hell--which can be found in most cultures. The stories, the myths and the twists and turns differ, and sometimes they take such fantastical turns that make it all seem like a fable.
